column3: 'title': [u"\n                    Geoffrey Beene Regular Fit Men's Trousers            "]
column12:
'desc': [u'

Geoffrey Beene Regular Fit Men's Trousers Price: Rs.600

Pep up your style quotient by wearing this brown striped pair of trousers from the house of Geoffrey Beene. The regular fit formal pant is made from a blend of polyester and viscose and gives you comfort all day long. The slant pockets in front and the welt pockets at the back give this pair of Geoffrey Beene Trousers a smart look. The flat fronted trouser enhances your attractiveness.

Team this classy wear with a formal checkered shirt and shoes and get ready to face your interview with ease and confidence. A brand that believes in and exercises humanitarianism
column13:
Geoffrey Beene has deservedly won appreciation. A have-it-all range of trousers from the brand gives you an excellent combination of superior fabrics and elegant styling.

Fabric Care

Machine wash this casual wear. Do not dry clean this pair of trousers. Avoid bleaching. Use warm iron on it to feel comfortable.

']
